Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Carrying an extra weapon will affect your Movement Speed.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Sometimes, even privileges can become obstacles. The key is knowing how to maximize benefits while avoiding pitfalls...

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Jetavie, go figure it out in actual combat.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: You have mastered the art of good timing.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: I have nothing else to teach you.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Wisdom is the source of virtues.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: All sins come from ignorance.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Rude intruder, atone here!

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: In battle, the one who takes control of the situation first gets the advantage.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: There's also the counterattack strategy—waiting for the enemy to make a mistake before delivering a final blow.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: You decide the approach you wish to take.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: Looks like you've mastered how to be in control of the battle...

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: You've beaten me in both tactics and strategy.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: Defeat me and prove your competence.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: Defeat me and prove you are worthy of that treasure.

Name: The Authority's Reflection
Text: Defeating me is out of your capability.

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: What do you think love is? And what about hatred?

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: Hatred alone won't let you end someone's life with a peaceful mind, because...

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: Hatred breeds fear, while love births courage.

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: Looks like... I managed to do it. Heh.

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: I've shown you everything. Please... leave.

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Passion's Reflection
Text: Even a great man would make mistakes. You won't always be this lucky.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: All sins come from ignorance.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Rude intruder, atone here!

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Tell me, darling, do you understand the power of emotions?

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: In battle, the first to lose their calm is often the one who loses.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Let your fear or rage reign—once the battle begins, revel in the bloodshed.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: That was just... incredibly powerful. Truly unforgettable.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Such pure violence and destruction... *chuckles*

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Trying to get away? Impossible.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: Dance with me and kiss despair.

Name: The Greed's Reflection
Text: You shall fall here, Lost Soul.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Your computing power may be impressive, but combat isn't just a workout routine...

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Both endurance and burst potential are key to victory.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Balancing the two isn't something you can achieve with brute force alone.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Such overpowering attacks...

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Maybe I'm not even worth mentioning anymore compared to who you are now.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: I shall bestow three prophecies on you.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Failure, destruction, regrets.

Name: The Strength's Reflection
Text: Take these curses.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: As they say, true martial prowess flows like water.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: Regardless of the style, fighting techniques aren't meant to be rigidly followed...

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: The essence of martial arts lies in its adaptability to any situation.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: What an impressive duel.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: You are already an exceptional warrior and combat expert.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: Looking for truth? I see...

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: But will you really find what you are looking for behind this door?

Name: The Pride's Reflection
Text: Sorry for running my mouth again... Then again, what difference does it make to a walking corpse like you?

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: A warrior without grit is like a sleeping lion.

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: Even with incredible skills...

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: Those who cannot hold onto their resolve are easily swayed by their enemies.

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: It looks like your determination is every bit as strong as mine.

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: Stay strong, and don't ever let go!

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Obsession's Reflection
Text: Hmph. Just another reckless fool, not even worth my time.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: All sins come from ignorance.

Name: The Sage's Reflection
Text: Rude intruder, atone here!

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: True strength comes from the unity of body and mind.

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: Even the weak can possess the heart of a hero...

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: One day, they too can become the master of their own destiny.

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: Such unwavering focus and perfected battle techniques...

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: That's why you're the Child of Miracles chosen by the Matrix.

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: Congratulations on your graduation, Jetavie.

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: Sure, you have experienced living, but have you experienced death?

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: I'll teach you, and don't forget it.

Name: The Sovereign's Reflection
Text: I'll teach you, and don't forget it.

Name: Jetavie
Text: Let's wreak some havoc together! Carriages are super fun! And hey—perform well and you might earn a bonus buff!

Name: Jetavie
Text: Flawless! Gain 40% extra DMG bonus!

Name: Jetavie
Text: So close, just a bit more. But you still gain 30% extra DMG bonus!

Name: Jetavie
Text: LAMEEEE! But you still gain 20% Extra DMG Bonus!
